{"tid":1304982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[法律JJ]  任何人可無需手令而逮捕任何他合理地懷疑犯了可逮捕的罪行的人","createTime":"2019-07-10T18:01:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T18:22:59.000Z","uid":26332,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c31d4b270368fd19ff65f7ac12125d35d4d9b3ac","tid":1304982,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:01:08.000Z","msg":"第221章 《刑事訴訟程序條例》 第101條 在某些案件中循簡易程序拘捕罪犯<br />\n<br />\n(2)任何人可無需手令而逮捕任何他合理地懷疑犯了可逮捕的罪行的人。<br />\n<br />\nCAP 221 CRIMINAL PROCEDURE ORDINANCE Section 101 Summary apprehension of offender in certain cases<br />\n<br />\n(2)Any person may arrest without warrant any person whom he may reasonably suspect of being guilty of an arrestable offence. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第101A條 作出逮捕時武力的使用等<br />\n<br />\n(1)任何人於防止罪案時或於進行或協助合法逮捕罪犯或疑犯或非法地不在羈留中的人時，可使用<strong><ins>就當時環境而言屬於合理</ins></strong>的武力。<br />\n<br />\n101A Use of force in making arrest, etc<br />\n<br />\n(1)A person may use such force as is reasonable in the circumstances in the prevention of crime or in effecting or assisting in the lawful arrest of offenders or suspected offenders or of persons unlawfully at large.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hklii.hk/eng/hk/legis/ord/221/s101.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklii.hk%2Feng%2Fhk%2Flegis%2Ford%2F221%2Fs101.html&d=RGEj3L6UPYZQbhamDwVV3QwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=682dbff3\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklii.hk/eng/hk/legis/ord/221/s101.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">各位都係良好巿民，見義勇為，有罪案發生除咗報警，緊急情況下普通人都可以進行逮捕，並之後交俾警方。</span></ins></strong>"},{"pid":"74a5b9206d471cb43834d71d8cddb5aef0f410ad","tid":1304982,"uid":275767,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:03:26.000Z","msg":"亂貼街招 係咪都要報警？"},{"pid":"a383e21e5dc1e9d5379bd266a9cb6714366a1d60","tid":1304982,"uid":26332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T18:04:03.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"ddd44d020